detailIntroText: Star Atlas is a next-gen gaming metaverse emerging from the confluence of state-of-the-art blockchain, real-time graphics, multiplayer video games, and decentralized financial technologies. It is being built on Unreal Engine 5, allowing for cinema-quality, real-time environments. Set in the year 2620, Star Atlas features a futuristic science fiction setting with three major factions competing for resources and control: humankind, a consortium of alien races, and sentient androids.
BloodLoop is a 5v5 Hero-Shooter game integrating Web3 technology, enhancing gameplay with a blockchain based on Avalanche Subnets.
Golden Tides is a fantasy pirate game where each player has unique abilities, form a pirate team, explore over 50 islands, meet NPCs, find treasures and pets, and participate in PVP.

Moonveil Studio is comprised of a team of seasoned professionals with extensive expertise in the gaming industry. The product includes Astrark: STAGE ONE is an immersive tower defense mobile game that centers around PvP and PVE battles, and cooperative multiplayer experiences. And Project B: A “stealth mode” game.

Otherside is a gamified, interoperable metaverse where players own the world, any NFT can become a playable character, and thousands of people can play together at the same time. The game blends mechanics from MMORPGs and Web3-enabled virtual worlds. An Otherdeed NFT represents more than a mere picture of land; it's an access token to participate in playtesting and co-creation of Otherside. Additionally, each Otherdeed NFT depicts a Plot of land that will be available in Otherside, with a unique composition of natural elements, resources, elemental attributes, and more.

SkyArk Chronicles is a Triple A fantasy JRPG game with interoperable NFTs. It is a trilogy consisting of two GameFi titles ("House of Heroes" and "Legends Arise") and one SocialFi metaverse ("Mirrorverse").
